						<summary>

						<p>This records an endowment of 80 <hi rend="italic">kāśu</hi> to the temple of Tirumāḍaippāṟai-Uḍaiyār by a certain Araśaṉ Vayiri of Eyil <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Rājēndraśōḻanallūr, for meeting the expenses of worship and procession of the image of Viṉāyaka-Piḷḷaiyār on the day of Āmāvāsya every month.</p>						

						</summary>
